Class Registration

java.lang.Object
com.flipfit.bean.Registration
public class Registration extends Object
Represents a user registration request in the FlipFit system. Used for storing details of both gym customers and gym owners during the initial registration or approval process.
Author:
team IOTA

    • Registration

      public Registration()
      Default constructor. Initializes the registration date to current time and sets approval status to false.

    • Registration

      public Registration(int registrationId, String name, String email, String password, String mobileNumber, String roleType)
      Parameterized constructor for creating a registration request with basic details.
      Parameters:
      registrationId - unique ID
      name - full name
      email - contact email
      password - raw password
      mobileNumber - 10-digit mobile
      roleType - requested role ("CUSTOMER" or "GYM_OWNER")
